---

<section class="stats-band rx">
  <div class="w">
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-box rxl d1">
        <div class="stat-label">Reduction in wasted marketing spend</div>
        <div class="stat-detail">Achieved by connecting all channels to retained client outcomes and cutting what doesn't move the needle.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-box rxl d2">
        <div class="stat-label">Increase in form-to-consultation rate</div>
        <div class="stat-detail">Intake process optimization closes the gap between lead volume and cases signed.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-box rxr d1">
        <div class="stat-label">ROI improvement after intake optimization</div>
        <div class="stat-detail">Marketing spend goes further when your intake system converts the leads you're already generating.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .stats-band {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--white);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.12);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.12);
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 48px;
  }

  .stat-box {
    padding: 0 0 0 20px;
    border-left: 3px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.4);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .stat-detail {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
</style>
